WT_XAML_Class_Factory Class Reference

#include <XamlClassFactory.h>

List of all members.

Detailed Description

Class factory for creating DWFx 2D graphics streams. We use the XAML moniker here, but technically our DWFx 2D streams are based on the WPF subset of XAML, not actually "full XAML".

See also:
